FreeBSD.  Added routine for date conversion.  Added entry for ``IP Addresses
vs. Host Names in Configuration File''.  Added new section about ``Various
Tricks'' (``Mixing Time Protocols'', ``Avoiding Time Steps'').  Revised section
about ``Computer Clocks''.  Added new entries for ``Solaris'' and ``Linux on
DEC Alpha''.  Added references to RFC 2783.</TD
></TR
><TR
><TD
